      Product description

      Stylus Pencil for iPad Pro 2021, iPad Air 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad Pro 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad 8th/7th/6th Generation, iPad mini 5

      Wide Compatibility
      iPad Pro 2021 12.9/11, iPad Air 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad Pro 4th & 3rd Generation 12.9/11, iPad 8th/7th/6th Generation, iPad mini 5.

      IPad Pro, IPad Air, IPad, IPad Mini 2018-2021
      Designed for these iPad tablets launched 2018 and after.

      How to use
      Double tap the cap to turn on, and double tap the cap to turn off.

      Tilt Creativity
      This pen contains tilt pressure sensors. The tilt angle reflects the different thickness and concentration of the line.

      Pixel precision
      Using advanced technology, the Stylus can accurately locate each pixel of the display and work like an A pple pencil

      Palm Rejection
      You can rest your palm on the tablet display while you write so that focus on the task at hand.

      Tap the Screen to make a quick note
      Tap your iPad display with the Stylus to open the Notes app and collect your ideas easily.

      Magnetic
      The Pencil can be magnetically stored aside the iPad Pro, iPad, iPad Air, iPad mini 2018-2021.

      Fast Charging
      High Capacity Lithium Battery. USB C fast charging. 1 minute = 30 minutes to use. charging time: less than 1 hour.

      Beauty
      A slim and elegant aluminum pencil body design.

      What You Get
      1* AZX Palm Rejection Active Pencil + 2* Additional Replacement Tips + 1* USB C Cable + 1* User manual.

      Warranty
      We Provide 12-Month Warranty AND Lifetime Technical Support.

      Product information

      Item Weight 0.5 ounces
